Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:06.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(410,450)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.41,0:01:05.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:05.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.16,0:01:06.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:06.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's quitting time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.21,0:01:09.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今晚有场牌要打
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:09.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a card game tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.08,0:01:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要跟谁打牌  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are you playing cards with, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:14.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(532,590)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.67,0:01:14.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去海之霸跟痞老板打
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:14.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l'm going over to the Chum Bucket to play with Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.13,0:01:16.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:16.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.59,0:01:17.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:17.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.89,0:01:19.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可是你的死对头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.89,0:01:19.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's your archenemy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.22,0:01:22.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,偷蟹黄堡秘方偷了有好多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:20.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's been trying to steal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:22.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Krabby Patty formula for years
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.27,0:01:27.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛跟他打牌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:27.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why would you play cards with him?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.28,0:01:28.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我告诉你  你别传出去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:28.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Between you and me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.91,0:01:32.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全裤头村里就属痞老板牌打得最烂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.91,0:01:32.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton is the worst card player in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.73,0:01:34.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十五年来  我每周四晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:34.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, I've been taking him to the cleaners
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.40,0:01:37.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都能把他钱都给赢走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:37.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,every Thursday night for 15 years
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.61,0:01:39.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不可能输
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:39.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never lose
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.96,0:01:54.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把他钱都赢走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:54.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Taking him to the cleaners
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.51,0:01:55.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:55.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's a hot one
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.22,0:01:58.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,昨天牌打得怎么样  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:58.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How'd the card game go last night, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.22,0:01:59.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:01:59.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lost
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.29,0:02:00.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,见鬼了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:00.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.76,0:02:02.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你输了多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:02.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How much money did you lose?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.06,0:02:03.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没输钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:03.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't lose any money
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.14,0:02:04.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:04.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lost
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.97,0:02:07.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万别说你输了蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:07.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you lost the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.44,0:02:08.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:08.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lost
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.27,0:02:09.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:09.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快说你没输掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,please tell me you didn't lose the
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡的秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.89,0:02:14.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:14.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.98,0:02:15.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,输了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:15.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lost
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.53,0:02:17.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:17.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.90,0:02:18.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:18.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.86,0:02:21.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我拿你当赌注  然后我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:21.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet your contract and I lost
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.99,0:02:25.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:25.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.40,0:02:27.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  我得去做蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:27.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I got to make those Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.84,0:02:37.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恐怕你再也不能在这工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:37.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid you don't work here anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.09,0:02:40.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快说你没在开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:40.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please tell me this isn't a joke
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.51,0:02:42.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说啊  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:42.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go on, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.04,0:02:43.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟他说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.04,0:02:43.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell him
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.02,0:02:46.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说你开的玩笑有多残忍恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:46.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell him all about your cruel, sick joke
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.30,0:02:49.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽管我特爱残忍恶心的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:49.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As much as I love cruel, sick jokes
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.48,0:02:51.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我恐怕他没开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:51.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid he's not joking
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.49,0:02:55.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在要给我工作了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:55.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You work for me now, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.66,0:03:00.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该戴上海之霸桶型工作头盔了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.66,0:03:00.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to put on the official Chum Bucket bucket helmet
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.24,0:03:04.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:04.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.66,0:03:06.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想给他工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:06.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to work for him
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.11,0:03:09.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要在这蟹堡王给你工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:09.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to work for you here at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.00,0:03:14.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:14.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.34,0:03:19.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到底会是怎样冷酷无情的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:19.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What kind of cold, heartless person
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.05,0:03:22.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会拆散这样充满爱的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:22.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would break apart such a loving relationship?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.86,0:03:36.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是你最大的失误  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:36.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is your greatest blunder, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.60,0:03:39.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十五年来  我玩牌就是为了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:39.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For 15 years, I've been throwing those card games
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等着你失手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just waiting for you to slip up
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.78,0:03:45.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然蟹黄堡秘方并没有到我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:45.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I may not have the precious Krabby Patty formula
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.48,0:03:47.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是我拥有第二好的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:47.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I've got the next best thing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.48,0:03:49.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是做蟹黄堡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:49.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the guy who makes them
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.04,0:03:51.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我马上就能让你倒闭了  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:51.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to run you out of business, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.58,0:03:55.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:55.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(338,682)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能把胳膊要回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I have my arms back?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:14.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(850,252)}科学
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.48,0:04:20.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  我准备好拿蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:20.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm ready for my Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.65,0:04:23.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:23.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Plankton, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.76,0:04:25.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:25.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能你还不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在在给我工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You work for me now
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,作为你的新老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and as your new boss
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.87,0:04:36.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我命令你马上给我做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:36.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I command you to make me a patty this instant
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.28,0:04:38.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,否则我就只能摘掉你的脑子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:38.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or I'll be forced to remove your brain
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.71,0:04:41.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,装到我的机器厨师里面去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:41.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and implant it in my robot chef
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就开始做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, get cooking
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(698,736)}厨房
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:56.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(698,736)}厨房
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牌子上面写着厨房
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sign says "kitchen"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:57.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(698,736)}厨房
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.61,0:04:59.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的心上却写着监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:59.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but my heart says "jail"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.45,0:05:13.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无论身在何处  炉台仍是炉台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:13.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A stove is a stove no matter where you go
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.28,0:05:20.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肉饼仍是肉饼  正是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:20.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A patty is a patty, that's what I say
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.29,0:05:23.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烤架仍是烤架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:23.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A grill is a grill
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.97,0:05:27.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:27.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is surely so
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.05,0:05:33.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无论如何  薯条仍是薯条
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:33.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And fries should be fries either way
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.64,0:05:37.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但这烤架不属于家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:37.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But this grill is not a home
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.24,0:05:40.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,炉台我也不熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:40.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is not the stove I know
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.82,0:05:47.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以把它换过去  只愿你能够回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:47.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would trade it all away if you'd come back to stay
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.86,0:05:54.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这间厨房没有你  不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:54.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This kitchen's not the same without you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.84,0:05:57.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是一家小破店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:57.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just a greasy spoon
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.08,0:06:01.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一家小破店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:06:01.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a greasy spoon
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.17,0:06:08.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:08.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Without you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.43,0:06:12.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:12.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,掉眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All these tears?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.19,0:06:15.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有乱唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:15.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the show tunes?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.92,0:06:18.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他怎么没在做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:18.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why isn't he making the patties?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.14,0:06:19.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:19.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.02,0:06:20.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,启用B计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:20.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going with Plan B
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把他脑子放到机器厨师里面去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll put his brain in the robot chef
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该要清楚那样子没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know that never works
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.65,0:06:27.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,答案很明显
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:27.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The answer is obvious
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.32,0:06:28.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要让海绵宝宝工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:28.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To get to the SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.70,0:06:31.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你必须要在他面前表现出同情与理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:31.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you must show him compassion and understanding
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.23,0:06:33.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样他就会给你想要的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:33.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then he'll give you what you want
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you be quiet?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.49,0:06:35.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还在想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:35.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.68,0:06:39.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要让海绵宝宝工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:39.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To get to the SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.37,0:06:42.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就得在他面前表现出同情与理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:42.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show him compassion and understanding
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样他就会给我想要的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then he'll give me what I want
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.50,0:06:49.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:49.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.63,0:06:50.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:50.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trying my best
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.73,0:06:54.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不习惯这样子做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:54.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not used to cooking this way
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.75,0:06:56.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你别把我脑子弄出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:56.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please don't take my brain out
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.77,0:07:00.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能同情和理解你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:00.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm capable of compassion and understanding
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.76,0:07:01.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:01.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.50,0:07:03.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我想要回蟹堡王去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:03.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then I'd like to go back to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.42,0:07:04.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别给我得寸进尺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:04.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's not get carried away
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.19,0:07:07.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我要怎样才能让你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:07.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, what can I do to make you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在海之霸工作得更舒服一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,more comfortable here at the Chum Bucket?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.88,0:07:11.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一般用烤架做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:11.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I usually cook on a grill
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.82,0:07:12.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:12.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.87,0:07:18.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽说不容易  但总算弄来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:18.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it wasn't easy, but here it is
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个旧烤架
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one old frying grill
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要试用下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about we try it out?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just that
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.29,0:07:26.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,习惯烤架朝那个方向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:26.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm used to the grill facing that way
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.44,0:07:27.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不必多说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:27.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say no more
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都会办妥的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of everything
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.55,0:07:33.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放这怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:33.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about here?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.76,0:07:35.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往左边一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:35.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little more to the left
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.97,0:07:38.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样呢  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:38.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's this, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.58,0:07:40.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再移一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:40.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Move it over a little more
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.52,0:07:43.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:43.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.23,0:07:44.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续移
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:44.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep going
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.36,0:07:46.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:46.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.41,0:07:48.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:48.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再移一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a little more
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.49,0:07:53.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:53.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.11,0:07:53.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就放这了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:53.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right there
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不太对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.45,0:07:59.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉哪里还是怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:59.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something still doesn't feel right
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再走几步  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a few more steps, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  可以摘眼罩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, go ahead, take it off
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.75,0:08:11.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边把蟹堡王厨房丝毫不差仿过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:11.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lt's an exact replica of the Krusty Krab kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.43,0:08:14.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是丝毫不差
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:14.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is an exact replica
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.52,0:08:15.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水池在这
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:15.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's the sink
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.71,0:08:17.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,油锅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:17.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The greasy fryers
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.10,0:08:18.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吱吱叫的地板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:18.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The squeaky floorboards
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.56,0:08:20.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有那个玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:20.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that thing
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.64,0:08:23.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份蟹黄堡马上来  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:23.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Krabby Patty coming up, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.48,0:08:27.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:27.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.94,0:08:29.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别哭了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:29.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.78,0:08:32.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要让你知道  给我工作比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:32.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show you it's much better working for me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.52,0:08:36.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有什么是那小气老螃蟹不让给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:33.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ls there anything
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:36.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that old skinflint Krabs wouldn't let you have?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.45,0:08:39.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有样东西我倒是一直很想要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:39.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, there is one thing l've always wanted
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你现在是不是心满意足
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, now do you have everything you need
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.96,0:08:47.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要开始做蟹黄堡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:47.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to make some Krabby Patties?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.79,0:08:49.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:49.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.35,0:08:51.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要开始做蟹黄堡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:51.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to make some patties?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.51,0:08:53.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我吃完冰淇淋再说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:53.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait till I finish my ice cream
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那蟹黄堡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about those patties?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.80,0:08:59.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再快点  再快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:59.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Faster, faster
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.14,0:09:02.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后最小的海精灵说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:02.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"And then the littlest sea elf said"
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.15,0:09:11.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冷静  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:11.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Steady, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.63,0:09:13.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就要有回报了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:13.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lt's all going to pay off soon enough
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.53,0:09:17.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  贪睡虫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:17.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey there, sleepyhead
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.49,0:09:18.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:18.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.73,0:09:21.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备来准备去的都让我饿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:21.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All that preparation is making me hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.17,0:09:22.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也好饿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:22.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.16,0:09:24.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得现在要吃什么最好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:24.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what would really hit the spot?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.48,0:09:27.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不你给咱做点蟹黄堡来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:27.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you whip us up a couple of Krabby Patties?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.71,0:09:30.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在比较想吃玉米卷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:30.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of in the mood for tacos
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.34,0:09:34.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错嘛  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:34.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.02,0:09:36.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是讲真  要不你去给咱做蟹黄堡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:36.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But really, why don't you go ahead and make us a patty
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.09,0:09:40.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  我不太想吃蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:40.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nah, I don't really feel like it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.40,0:09:41.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真就不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:41.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.26,0:09:44.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烤架你有了  锅铲你有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:44.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have the grill and the spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舒服椅子你有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the comfy chair
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.68,0:09:47.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的臭脚我按摩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:47.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I rubbed your putrid feet
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.73,0:09:48.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟你讲  小东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:48.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell you what, half-pint
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会再叫我做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why don't you ask me later?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.32,0:09:54.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我命令你马上给我做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:54.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I command you to make me a patty this instant
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.30,0:09:57.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别给我顶嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:57.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't back- sass me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.03,0:10:02.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:02.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it, mister
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你已经无权拥有脑子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just lost your brain privileges
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.37,0:10:09.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:09.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finished
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.75,0:10:12.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  快进来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:12.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, come in here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.21,0:10:19.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是应该要改叫机器海绵厨师宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:19.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or should I say RobotBob SpongeChefPants?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都把脑子放到机器里面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l put the brain in the robot, you know
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就不该这么娇生惯养
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have been a spoiled brat
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.12,0:10:27.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧  我要什么就能有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:27.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see, I always get what I want
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.05,0:10:30.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在就要你给我做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:30.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I want you to make me a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.61,0:10:36.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回答  等会再叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:36.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Response: Why don't you ask me later?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.67,0:10:39.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:39.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.17,0:10:40.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去做焊接了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:40.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get welded
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.54,0:10:41.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:41.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.37,0:10:44.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我命令你给我做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:44.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I command you, make me a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1104,800)}油
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:50.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(322,356)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:57.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(950,390)}停业
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.21,0:10:53.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老宝贝  我们要就此完结了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:53.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, old girl, this looks like our final chapter
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也忍不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't take anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.80,0:11:02.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得把那个黄色噩梦带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:02.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got to take that yellow nightmare back
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.07,0:11:03.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就不值得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:03.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not worth it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.58,0:11:07.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还是回去光明正大偷你蟹黄堡才好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:07.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm better off stealing a Krabby Patty fair and square
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:07.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(938,632)}停业
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.98,0:11:12.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经都说好了  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:12.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, a deal's a deal, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.06,0:11:14.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他现在是你的麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:14.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's your headache now
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.94,0:11:17.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你大发慈悲吧  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:17.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please have mercy, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.94,0:11:18.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么都可以做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:18.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.19,0:11:20.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I beg of you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.72,0:11:23.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不你给我五十块
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:23.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about you give me 50 bucks
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.61,0:11:24.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把他从你那买回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:24.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll take him off your hands?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.87,0:11:25.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成交
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:25.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a deal
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正我也抽老千了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I cheated anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.49,0:11:29.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在快走吧  小虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:29.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, begone with you, you puny pest
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.21,0:11:33.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:33.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.88,0:11:39.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟我脑子很高兴能回来  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:39.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My brain and I are glad to be back, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴你回来了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good to have you back, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.83,0:11:42.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:42.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, get to those patties
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.70,0:11:44.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,午餐高峰要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:44.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The lunch rush is a-coming
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.06,0:11:47.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不太想做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:47.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.45,0:11:49.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会再说吧  蟹哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:49.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask me later, Krabby?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我意思是  我今天白干活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm working all day for free
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.76,0:11:56.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要工钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:56.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my treat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:59.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(278,356)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.11,0:11:58.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:58.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought you said
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:02.61,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(313,305)}铅笔人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:04.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(466,394)\frz21.13}导演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:08.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:06.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz21.13\pos(318,534)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:08.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz21.13\pos(416,294)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:10.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz21.13\pos(308,336)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:10.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz21.13\pos(480,658)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:10.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.33,0:12:13.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看啊  这是在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:13.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, well, what is this?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.54,0:12:17.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  是海上的画家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:17.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, the artist at sea
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们来看看他辛勤创作的成果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let us watch and see the fruits of his struggle
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,似乎他的灵感迸发出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It seems as if inspiration has struck
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铅笔  怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The pencil, what?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.53,0:12:42.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,画家学到了在海上的第一堂课
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:42.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The artist has learned the first lesson of the sea
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.67,0:12:44.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,备用铅笔一定要带好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:44.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Always bring a spare pencil
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.82,0:12:48.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:48.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.24,0:12:54.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了吗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.24,0:12:54.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ready, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.37,0:12:55.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:55.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.35,0:12:56.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:56.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.16,0:12:57.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:57.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,剪刀赢布  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scissors beats paper, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.47,0:13:05.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:05.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.51,0:13:06.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:06.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.76,0:13:07.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:07.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.89,0:13:12.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你怎么老是出布
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:12.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, how come you always do paper?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是个什么东西  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is that thing, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.95,0:13:30.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像是根大铅笔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:30.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lt looks like a giant pencil
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.73,0:13:32.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去摸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:32.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go touch it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.58,0:13:36.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是根大铅笔  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:36.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is a giant pencil, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.37,0:13:39.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来用这铅笔画大画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:39.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's draw some giant pictures with it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.56,0:13:40.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在画什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:40.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What you drawing?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.82,0:13:42.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,退后  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:42.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stand back, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你往我脖子哈气  我画都画不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't draw with you breathing down my neck
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.51,0:13:46.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好个画家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:46.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Artists
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.63,0:13:48.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,画的是水母
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:48.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.18,0:13:50.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还挺好看  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:50.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty good, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.78,0:13:53.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过这画缺乏基础结构
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:53.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it's lacking basic construction
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.60,0:13:56.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的透视仍有较多不足之处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:56.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and your perspective leaves a lot to be desired
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.39,0:13:58.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人人都会乱评价
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:58.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody's a critic
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.19,0:14:02.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你的画有生命力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:02.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, your drawing's coming to life
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.70,0:14:04.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这还差不多  批评家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:04.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's more like it, Mr. Critic
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  我意思是它游走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I mean it's swimming away
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道这样子什么意思吗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you know what this means, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.88,0:14:12.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的画没法挂进博物馆了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:12.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your art can never hang in a museum
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.49,0:14:16.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意思就是我们找到了根神奇铅笔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:16.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It means we found a magic pencil
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.79,0:14:19.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在就只要个神奇小胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:19.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now all I need is a magic moustache
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.52,0:14:22.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我所有梦想就会全都实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:22.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and all my dreams will have come true
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.59,0:14:24.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:24.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming right up
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.26,0:14:27.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生活真美好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:27.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Life is good
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来得快去得也快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Easy come, easy go
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.22,0:14:34.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  要是你长了头发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:34.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, if you had some hair
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.64,0:14:37.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就会是全海洋最帅的生物了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:37.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'd be the most gorgeous creature in the sea
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.91,0:14:40.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你长相好  才艺棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:40.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got looks, talent
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.66,0:14:43.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万事俱备  只欠满头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:43.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all you need is a full head of
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.41,0:14:44.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秀发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:44.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hair
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.40,0:14:45.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轮我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:45.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My turn
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.50,0:14:46.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心点  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:46.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当画家责任重大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Being an artist is a heavy responsibility
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.54,0:14:53.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,作的每幅画好比孩童  必须悉心呵护
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:51.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Each work of art is like a child
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:53.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and must be treated as such
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.18,0:14:56.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  我只是要画漫画而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:56.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, I was just going to draw a cartoon
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.05,0:14:57.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你咋不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:57.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, why didn't you say so?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又画了只水母
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.29,0:15:03.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,画的是章鱼哥  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:03.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Squidward, silly
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.55,0:15:08.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它动起来看着有点吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:08.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's kind of creepy-looking when it moves
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.05,0:15:10.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得对  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:10.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.55,0:15:12.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能放它进城
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:12.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't let him go into town
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.60,0:15:18.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:18.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poor Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.39,0:15:22.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚想出了个好点子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:22.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My brain just hatched an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.74,0:15:32.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这绝对会超经典的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:32.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is going to be classic
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.82,0:15:36.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去公园散散步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:36.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I fancy a stroll around the park
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.04,0:15:38.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:38.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.25,0:15:40.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们要搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:40.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.52,0:15:42.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:42.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, what's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.33,0:15:45.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人送钱让我烫发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:45.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone left me some money for a perm
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.30,0:15:49.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快让我多发帅哥拿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:49.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come to Hairy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.47,0:15:55.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:55.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my hair
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.05,0:15:58.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:58.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.39,0:16:02.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:02.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又有点子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got another idea
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这回的恶作剧是终极版
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This'll be the ultimate prank
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.54,0:16:11.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我画我自己  然后章鱼哥一开门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:11.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l'll draw me, and when Squidward answers the door
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.50,0:16:13.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,门外的就不是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:13.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it won't be me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看人家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at him
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.19,0:16:18.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好俊俏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:18.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ain't he a doll?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.47,0:16:19.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是差了个领带
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:19.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All he needs is a tie
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备行动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready for action
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他走到门口了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's going to the door
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在敲门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's knocking at the door
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.01,0:16:39.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥应门  然后就
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:39.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's answering the door, and
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.39,0:16:44.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在打章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:44.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's beating up Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.52,0:16:49.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铅笔人  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:49.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doodle Boy, stop
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他抢到铅笔了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's got the pencil
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.70,0:17:01.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都干什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:01.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.98,0:17:03.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须要找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:03.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to find him
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可能会在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where could he possibly be?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.98,0:17:09.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能是在那间潦草的菠萝屋里面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:09.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's in that poorly drawn pineapple
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.05,0:17:11.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:11.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不要进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not going in there
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.43,0:17:16.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:16.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.54,0:17:17.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就待在你身后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:17.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm right behind you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.69,0:17:18.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小步走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.69,0:17:18.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Baby steps
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.31,0:17:23.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:23.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost there
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚那是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  把我抬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Patrick, give me a boost up
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.40,0:17:42.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱就不能待在这安全的地方里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:42.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't we just stay down here where it's safe?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.04,0:17:42.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:42.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.79,0:17:44.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这怪物出自我之手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:44.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I created this monster
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.24,0:17:45.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我必须要阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:45.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I've got to stop him
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懂我意思了吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See what I mean, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.68,0:17:52.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪儿泄露了  大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:52.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's the leak, ma'am?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You okay, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,芬兰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finland
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.61,0:18:19.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就在那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:19.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There he is
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.84,0:18:21.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他丑死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:21.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's hideous
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.16,0:18:23.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看到他我就想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:23.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He makes me sick just looking at him
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大凸眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those big, bulgy eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.14,0:18:29.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方身体  俩龅牙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:29.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that square body, those two buck teeth
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.41,0:18:31.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笨领带
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:31.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and that stupid tie
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.25,0:18:35.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过在你身上就很好看  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:35.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it looks good on you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.72,0:18:38.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他把铅笔放下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:38.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's putting down the pencil
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.96,0:18:40.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时机到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:40.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is our chance
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.64,0:18:41.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我数到三
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:41.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On the count of three
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(874,920)}惊 喜
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就一起跳出去袭击他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we'll jump out and surprise him
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.01,0:18:44.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然有个惊喜派对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:44.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, a surprise party
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.88,0:18:46.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天他生日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:46.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it his birthday?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.84,0:18:51.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:51.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do something
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.55,0:18:52.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:52.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.69,0:18:55.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,礼物送你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:55.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your present
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.11,0:18:57.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:57.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're welcome
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在那站好  铅笔人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there, Doodle
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.18,0:19:04.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把你带到了这个世上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:04.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I brought you into this world
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.15,0:19:07.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我要把你赶出这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:07.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now I'm going to take you out
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.01,0:19:08.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有遗言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:08.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any last words?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  说的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, what was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.09,0:19:22.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要动  铅笔人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:22.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold still, Doodle
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这都是为了你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is for your own good
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.83,0:19:26.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尝尝那招  还有这招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:26.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take that, and this
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.47,0:19:27.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有这招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:27.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and this
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.06,0:19:28.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有那招  还有这招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:28.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and that, and this
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.47,0:19:30.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那招这招那招这招那招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:30.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that, this, that, this, that
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.48,0:19:41.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是海绵宝宝  铲除邪恶之人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:41.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l am SpongeBob, destroyer of evil
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.74,0:19:42.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:42.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it easy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.74,0:19:43.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一幅画而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:43.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's just a drawing
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.24,0:19:46.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正完事了  对吧派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:46.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that takes care of that, eh, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.47,0:19:48.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:48.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Done and done
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.24,0:19:57.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你真早该得过去看看的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:57.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, Gary, you should have been there
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.11,0:19:58.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的特刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:58.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It sure was exciting
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.49,0:20:01.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过其实  我有点想念铅笔人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:01.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, you know, I kind of miss the little doodle
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.31,0:20:02.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就像是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.31,0:20:02.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was like a son to me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.82,0:20:04.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正我很高兴一切都正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:04.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I am glad that things are back to normal
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.39,0:20:08.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安了  小王子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:08.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, good night, sweet prince
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:10.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1244,932)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.27,0:20:11.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安了  神奇铅笔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:11.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, magic pencil
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.09,0:20:38.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神奇铅笔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:38.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, magic pencil
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.09,0:20:39.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:39.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing up?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给自己画杯水喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Drawing yourself a glass of water?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.01,0:20:44.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铅笔人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:44.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,DoodleBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.34,0:20:47.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该没有生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:47.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No hard feelings, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.48,0:20:52.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你到底想干什么  铅笔人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:52.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing, Doodle?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.31,0:20:54.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你铅笔人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:54.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You Doodle
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.66,0:21:16.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心点使那玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:16.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be careful with that thing
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.37,0:21:17.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁知道会有什么后果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:17.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who knows what will happen?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.13,0:21:21.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鼻子知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:21.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knows
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.97,0:21:32.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,觉得很好笑吧  铅笔人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:32.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very funny, Doodle
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.23,0:21:34.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在轮我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:34.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it's my turn
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.36,0:21:44.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铅笔人  看来这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:44.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Doodle, it looks like this
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:45.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(774,920)}作 画
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.55,0:21:45.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才叫扯平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:45.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is a draw
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:51.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(714,920)}也 有 笔 尖
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.66,0:21:51.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说到重点了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:51.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've made your point
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.24,0:21:55.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正没事  我高中公认美术最好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:55.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No matter, I was voted "most artistic" in high school
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.33,0:22:00.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你要给我付出代价
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:00.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you're going to pay for that
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.84,0:22:02.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,似乎是公认最笨拙才对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:02.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was "most clumsy"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.48,0:22:20.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,纸张
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:20.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Paper
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.82,0:22:23.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给铅笔人先生来一页
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:23.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Page for Mr. Doodle
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.44,0:22:36.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  这乱糟糟的是怎一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.44,0:22:36.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, what's with all the ruckus?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.97,0:22:38.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己来看吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.97,0:22:38.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a look for yourself, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.54,0:22:41.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是那个邪恶的涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:41.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the evil doodle
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.06,0:22:43.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错了  不邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.06,0:22:43.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, not evil
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.01,0:22:45.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他只是个二维生物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.01,0:22:45.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was just a two-dimensional creature
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.13,0:22:47.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在我们的三维海底世界迷了路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:47.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lost in our three-dimensional aquatic world
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.78,0:22:49.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,寻求自己命中的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.78,0:22:49.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,longing for a purpose
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.84,0:22:50.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:50.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.26,0:22:52.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就一副画了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.26,0:22:52.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's a drawing?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.40,0:22:53.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.40,0:22:53.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exactly
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.74,0:22:55.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看人家多开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:55.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See how happy he is?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.93,0:22:57.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是看着有点吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:22:57.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He still looks kind of creepy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.69,0:23:00.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,伟大的神奇铅笔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:00.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,O great magic pencil
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.33,0:23:02.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们海洋生物无法驾驭你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.33,0:23:02.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your powers are too mighty for us ocean dwellers
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.99,0:23:06.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,故我要把你送回你原先的神奇王国去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.99,0:23:04.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I will send you back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.32,0:23:06.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the magic kingdom from where you came
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.37,0:23:07.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.37,0:23:07.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.22,0:23:08.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:08.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.04,0:23:19.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们回过来看这深陷创作低谷的画家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.04,0:23:19.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We rejoin the artist in a creative slump
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.25,0:23:23.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:23.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.00,0:23:23.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:23.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:24.92,0:23:26.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的铅笔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:26.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My pencil
Dialogue: 1,0:23:32.09,0:23:35.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海上画家的第二条重要规则就是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:35.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The second most important rule for the artist at sea
Dialogue: 1,0:23:35.89,0:23:38.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,转笔刀一定要带好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:38.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Always bring a pencil sharpener
Dialogue: 1,0:23:39.52,0:23:42.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:42.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
